# Claude Code Native Memory

claude-mem was uninstalled on 2026-03-08. Claude Code has built-in persistent memory.

**Auto memory location**: `~/.claude/projects/<project>/memory/MEMORY.md`
- Loaded automatically at session start (first 200 lines)
- Claude writes its own notes here based on corrections and patterns
- Run `/memory` in Claude Code to view, edit, or toggle

**Task tracking**: See `@TASKS.md` at project root for current sprint and next steps (if present).

